{"tid":2116577,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"香港首個科技指數上線啦!!!  追縱30大科技港股","createTime":"2020-07-20T08:53:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T12:58:34.000Z","uid":66271,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ce11345bb4b05d854f3f54d69fa9cb476c5f46c3","tid":2116577,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T08:53:20.000Z","msg":"「ATMX」等中資科網股近月交投、股價大升，恒指公司早前透露，短期內推出科技及創新指數，被視為「港股納指」。恒指公司周一公布，7月27日（星期一）推出恒生科技指數。新指數將會追蹤經篩選後最大30間於香港上市的科技企業，「ATMX」4大股份權重合計達33.49%。<br />\n<br />\n根據回溯測試計算數據，恒生科技指數於 2019 年全年及 2020 年上半年的回報分別高達 36.2%及 35.3%。<br />\n<br />\n恒指公司董事兼研究及分析主管黃偉雄本月稱，有關指數將參考納斯達克等科技股主題指數，冀成為繼恒指及國指後，另一受市場歡迎的指數。<br />\n<br />\n據恒指公司資料，阿里巴巴&nbsp;（09988）&nbsp;權重最高，佔8.53%，騰訊&nbsp;（00700）&nbsp;僅次佔8.52%，美團點評&nbsp;（03690）&nbsp;則佔8.33%，小米&nbsp;（01810）&nbsp;佔8.11%。<br />\n手機設備股，舜宇光學科技&nbsp;（02382）&nbsp;就佔8.02%，排行第5。"},{"pid":"fef22262644555a75f630081ac9a8fef4ed53191","tid":2116577,"uid":12463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T08:55:49.000Z","msg":"ETF？"},{"pid":"71d254f926640f20d9241219255e3c077862d4e7","tid":2116577,"uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T08:58:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/07/20/FTfdc2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F07%2F20%2FFTfdc2.png&h=3e7c0870&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64d87964e631940f0ceb4de0a16d2fef19f0f26e","tid":2116577,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71d254f926640f20d9241219255e3c077862d4e7","tid":2116577,"uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T08:58:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/07/20/FTfdc2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F07%2F20%2FFTfdc2.png&h=3e7c0870&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T09:01:01.000Z","msg":"升呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br